how can i lose the fat on my inner thighs and tighten my abs when we want to get rid of body fat there is no way to specifically burn fat from one part of the body doing situps won't burn the fat that is covering your abs and doing tricep extensions won't get rid of the fat that is covering your triceps the only thing you can do is lose weight all around and eventually the problem area will also improve the way to burn fat is through a calorie restricted diet in conjunction with an exercise routine that will burn calories activities that burn calories include running biking swimming and other high intensity activities guide to reducing body fat http www straighthealth com pages guides reducebodyfat html Dieting Atkins Nutritional Approach Weight training Calorie restriction Calorie Bodybuilding Exercise Obesity Low-carbohydrate diet Weight loss Anorexia nervosa Milk HyperText Transfer Protocol Swimming World Wide Web Elbow-joint Super Size Me Aerobic exercise Insulin South Beach diet Breastfeeding Fat Triathlon Nutrition Tocopherol Hormone replacement therapy (trans) Healthy eating Life extension Hyperglycemia Humerus Equine conformation Food guide pyramid Omega-3 fatty acid Physical attractiveness MyPyramid Uniform Resource Locator Body mass index Urinary incontinence Weight Watchers Osteoarthritis HTML Carburetor Cascading Style Sheets Prostate cancer Gastric bypass surgery Zone diet Motorcycle Filename extension Veganism Mountain bike JavaServer Pages Adipose tissue Professional wrestling throws XML Character encodings in HTML Asthma SAML Censorship in Australia Carpal tunnel syndrome Body image Dietary fiber Body type (exercise) Scapula Infantilism Macular degeneration HTML element Vegetarianism Glycogen storage disease type I Hypercholesterolemia Egg (food) Diabetes mellitus Thermoregulation Coronary heart disease Slim Fast Ghetto Qigong Explosive material Automobile Hypertension Thin client Growth hormone Tightlacing Drag racing Cat Hypoglycemia Website Mozill